Files were compiled and edited from four data sets. Source data includes existing_MPAS.shp, dfg_lands_m_acquired.shp, stprkalb27.shp, and CI_mpa.shp. All of California's designated marine protected areas with associated DFG fishing regulations for 2004 were selected and merged into one shapefile.
